reviews.review_text:
Only 1st Set 'The Weight'? I Think so... Great setlist, great show.

Thanks for the upgrade. Matrix sound cleans up the flaws that the raw SBD sources otherwise are maimed by. So cool that these tapes are being restored to their best possible status. 

Killer!

Thanks to the Wharf Rats! I attended this run of shows.  The first night was just average in my opinion.  However, the second night when we got to the venue our Wharf Rat buddy had heard the soundcheck and reported happily that they had played a "Death Don't Have No Mercy"!  We were jazzed about that and totally looking for it.  The moment when people realized what a treat we were getting that night right there was beautiful.  It was a good show.  Nice mix of songs and good playing.
